<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10279800>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Progress of alpha taxonomic studies on Isometopinae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10279800/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10279802>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Habitus of representatives of five extant Isometopinae tribes. A. Diphleps unica Bergroth, 1924 (Diphlebini); B. Bruneimetopus simulans Taszakowski, Kim & Herczek, 2020 (Gigantometopini); C. Isometopus mirificus Mulsant & Rey, 1879 (Isometopini); D. Myiomma milleri (Hoberlandt, 1959) (Myiommini); E. Sophianus palawanensis Taszakowski, Kim & Herczek, 2021 (Sophianini)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10279802/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10279804>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Living specimens of Isometopinae in their natural habitat (Singapore). A & B. Gigantometopus spp.; C. Unknown Gigantometopini; D & E. Unknown Isometopini; F. Isometopus sp., nymph; G. Alcecoris sp.; H. Alcecoris sp., nymph. Photo credits: David Ball (A, D); Melvyn Yeo (B, C, G, H); KS Tan (E, F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10279804/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10279806>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Fossil representatives of Isometopinae. A. Electromyiomma polonicum; B. Archemyiomma schaeferi; C. Hoffheinsoria robusta; D, E. Clavimyiomma henryi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10279806/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

